==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*χάρισμα / charisma / char'-is-mah
From [[χαρίζομαι]]; a (divine) gratuity, that is, deliverance (from danger or passion); (specifically) a (spiritual) endowment, that is, (subjectively) religious qualification, or (objectively) miraculous faculty: 

===Noun===
'''χάρισμα'''

# (free) [[gift]].

